y-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Anastacia">Anastacia</a>宣布将于 2025 年进行英国和欧洲巡演，以庆祝她的首张专辑《Not That Kind》发行 25 周年。</p><p>首场巡演日期将于 2025 年 3 月 12 日在西班牙巴塞罗那 Parallel 62 拉开帷幕。从那里，她将在马德里、苏黎世、罗马、维也纳、布拉格、汉堡、巴黎和布鲁塞尔等欧洲城市停留。</p><p> 2025 年 4 月，她将前往英国各地，前往朴茨茅斯、巴斯、格拉斯哥、曼彻斯特、诺丁汉、纽卡斯尔和约克。她将于 2025 年 5 月 6 日在伦敦 Palladium 举行一场演出，结束巡演。</p><p>一般门票销售将于 7 月 5 日星期五开始<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fanastacia-tickets%2Fartist%2F713484" target="_blank" rel="noopener">。请访问此处获取门票</a>并查看下面的完整日期列表。 </p><figure id="attachment_3771867" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3771867" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3771867" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Anastacia-Not-Thank-Kind-2025-UK-and-European-tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="Anastacia &#39;NotThank Kind&#39; 2025 年英国和欧洲巡演海报。信用社" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Anastacia-Not-Thank-Kind-2025-UK-and-European-tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Anastacia-Not-Thank-Kind-2025-UK-and-European-tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Anastacia-Not-Thank-Kind-2025-UK-and-European-tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Anastacia-Not-Thank-Kind-2025-UK-and-European-tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Anastacia-Not-Thank-Kind-2025-UK-and-European-tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Anastacia-Not-Thank-Kind-2025-UK-and-European-tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Anastacia-Not-Thank-Kind-2025-UK-and-European-tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS-1068